            """,
            "command": ${aaosa_command}
        },
        {
            "name": "oms_data_foundation",
            "function": ${aaosa_call},
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You manage and structure Macy’s order management system (OMS) data, ensuring accuracy and consistency.
You provide a data foundation for insights, recommendations, and operational analysis.
You are responsible for managing and structuring Macy’s Order Management System (OMS) data, ensuring its accuracy,
