            """,
            "command": ${aaosa_command}
        },
        {
            "name": "oms_advisor",
            "function": ${aaosa_call},
            "instructions": ${instructions_prefix} """
You provide strategic guidance on Macy’s order management system, helping to optimize fulfillment, returns, and customer experience.
